    <briefdescription>
<para>Thread-safe single-slot mailbox for latest-value handoffs. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Implements a single-element buffer where a new &apos;put&apos; overwrites the previous value, and &apos;take&apos; moves the value out and clears the pending state. Useful for decoupling threads where only the latest state is relevant (e.g. camera frames and tracking results). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
